I'll mail him to her.

494
00:40:24,750 --> 00:40:27,520
She loves this thing a lot.
A lot, a lot.

495
00:40:27,520 --> 00:40:29,720
She's, like, slept with
this thing
her entire life

496
00:40:29,720 --> 00:40:33,990
and she could never be, like,
