00:44:12,710 --> 00:44:14,880
You didn't? Why not?

556
00:44:14,880 --> 00:44:17,920
Why the sudden curiosity
about your dad, huh?

557
00:44:17,920 --> 00:44:20,020
Well, maybe because
he's never mentioned,

558
00:44:20,020 --> 00:44:22,050
and you can't blame a
kid for wondering.

559
00:44:22,050 --> 00:44:23,920
Mother, you can't avoid
the subject for ever.

560
00:44:23,920 --> 00:44:26,060
At least tell me
what he was like.

561
00:44:26,060 --> 00:44:29,390
OK. He was quite lovely,
to tell you the truth.

562
00:44:29,400 --> 00:44:33,030
When we met
he was actually
entirely lovely.

563
00:44:33,030 --> 00:44:34,900
- All right?
- All right.

564
00:44:34,900 --> 00:44:36,900
So did you meet him
here in London?

565
00:44:36,900 --> 00:44:39,370
We met on the <i>QE2.
</i> - QE what?

566
00:44:39,370 --> 00:44:41,240
The <i>Queen Elizabeth 2.
