00:44:48,050 --> 00:44:50,920
We were seated next to each
other at dinner.

571
00:44:50,920 --> 00:44:53,080
- He's an American, you know.
- No kidding?

572
00:44:53,090 --> 00:44:56,390
So, was it love at
first sight?

