What's wrong?

643
00:49:34,530 --> 00:49:37,400
Nothing. It's just I'm so
happy to be home.

644
00:49:37,400 --> 00:49:39,970
Hey, did I hear
something about corn
bread and chili?

645
00:49:39,970 --> 00:49:43,680
