646
00:49:43,680 --> 00:49:47,680
Something's changed
about you, Hal. Hm.
I can't put my finger on it,

647
00:49:47,680 --> 00:49:50,550
but something about you
has definitely changed.

648
00:49:50,550 --> 00:49:55,190
Really? Well, it's just the
same old me.

649
00:49:55,190 --> 00:49:55,550
- Honest.
- <i>(dog barks)</i>

650
00:49:57,260 --> 00:49:59,660
Hi, Sammy!

651
00:50:03,460 --> 00:50:06,630
