667
00:51:04,820 --> 00:51:06,390
Hal, it is none of my business
how your

668
00:51:06,390 --> 00:51:08,760
father makes a fool out of
himself, OK?

669
00:51:08,760 --> 00:51:10,500
- He's a big boy. He can do
