675
00:51:33,620 --> 00:51:37,090
Look, you and I both know
your father's not some
kind of suave, debonair,

676
00:51:37,090 --> 00:51:39,290
bachelor-of-the-month type.

677
00:51:39,290 --> 00:51:41,730
So I gotta ask myself,
what does a hot young thing
like that

678
00:51:41,730 --> 00:51:44,460
see in a guy who walks around
with his shirttail hanging out

679
00:51:44,460 --> 00:51:47,400
