They ride together, they
swim together.

687
00:52:08,190 --> 00:52:10,620
They go out to eat
dinner every night.

688
00:52:10,620 --> 00:52:15,490
Do you know what?
Meet her. See for yourself.
Don't let me influence you.

689
00:52:15,490 --> 00:52:16,290
There's my girl. Honey,
I want you to meet a
friend of mine.

690
00:52:20,670 --> 00:52:23,640
Hal, this is Meredith Blake.

691
00:52:28,210 --> 00:52:31,140
Hi.

692
00:52:31,140 --> 00:52:34,180
Hi... Meredith Blake.

693
00:52:34,180 --> 00:52:38,380
Wow, I can't believe
I'm finally meeting the
famous Hallie.

694
00:52:38,380 --> 00:52:41,920
- I have looked forward
to this all summer.
- Really? Well, here I am.

695
00:52:41,920 --> 00:52:44,820
Oh, Nicky, she's adorable.

696
00:52:44,820 --> 00:52:46,490
You know, the way your
father talked about you,

697
00:52:46,490 --> 00:52:48,560
I expected to meet
a little girl,

698
00:52:48,560 --> 00:52:50,630
but you are so grown-up.

699
00:52:50,630 --> 00:52:51,260
I'll be 12 soon.
How old are you?

700
00:52:53,330 --> 00:52:55,230
26.

701
00:52:56,770 --> 00:53:00,300
Only 15 years older than me.
How old are you again, Dad?

702
00:53:00,310 --> 00:53:03,540
